Title: Lil Nas X Feat. Billy Ray Cyrus: Old Town Road
Genre: Short, Adventure, Comedy, Music, Sci-Fi, Western
Actors: Lil Nas X, Billy Ray Cyrus, Chris Rock, Haha Davis
Plot: Music video for Lil Nas X's song Old Town Road (Remix) feat. Billy Ray Cyrus. Old West outlaws, Nas and Cyrus, get teleported from 1889 to 2019, where they interact with baffled residents of present day Old Town Road in entertaining ways.
